{"tid":240180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓電台再發出暗號廣播","createTime":"2017-05-12T08:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T08:52:44.000Z","uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4bf74347289fec462b9338deb39d697dc432e8a","tid":240180,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:41:44.000Z","msg":"北韓電台再次發出暗號廣播。<br />\n<br />\n平壤廣播電台凌晨播報「向探險隊隊員佈置外語課程複習作業」，之後讀出一連串數字，韓聯社表示，這些數字組合是第一次出現，內容和以往不同，可能是向於南韓潛伏的間諜傳達指令。<br />\n<br />\n北韓去年6月重啟停止了十六年的暗號廣播，至今已發出36次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1330054-20170512.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1330054-20170512.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b7d32122\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1330054-20170512.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=780db8e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1330054-20170512.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n連登神探 又有工開啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d780cf6600253f3b321242d4cbb32a51bd6606","tid":240180,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:50:51.000Z","msg":"有冇錄音?"},{"pid":"b7c887aecc82e2f7fef1efcc7280124e02fd6c5b","tid":240180,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}